MALACAÑANG Manila

PROCLAMATION NO. 722

CREATING AND DESIGNATING LIMA TECHNOLOGY CENTER (PHASE II), SITUATED IN THE BARANGAYS OF SANTIAGO & SAN FERNANDO, MUNICIPALITY OF MALVAR, PROVINCE OF BATANGAS, ISLAND OF LUZON, AS SPECIAL ECONOMIC ZONE PURSUANT TO REPUBLIC ACT NO. 7916 AS AMENDED BY REPUBLIC ACT 8748

Pursuant to the powers vested in me under Republic Act No. 7916, the Special Economic Zone Act of 1995 as amended by Republic Act No. 8748 and upon recommendation of the Board of Directors of the Philippine Economic Zone Authority, I, GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO , President of the Republic of the Philippines, by virtue of the powers vested in me by law, do hereby create and designate as Special Economic Zone , subject to the provisions of Republic Act No. 7916, as amended, its Implementing Rules and Regulations, and Resolution No. 96-341 dated 16 October 1996 of the PEZA Board of Directors, the Lima Technology Center (Phase II) located in the Barangays of Santiago and San Fernando, Municipality of Malvar, Province of Batangas, Island of Luzon, consisting an area of ONE MILLION FOUR HUNDRED NINETY EIGHT THOUSAND FOUR HUNDRED TWENTY THREE (1,498,423) SQUARE METERS , more or less, as defined by the following technical description:

